---
title: Spicy Pak Choi Ramen with coriander and optional egg
description: This spicy Asian-inspired veggie soup is the perfect cure for those altogether too-long evenings when you just can't seem to shake the cold. Serve with a perfectly soft-boiled egg for an added comfort factor.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W04_IE_IEVCLV13334-2_KB_Main_high-49000031.jpg
